item.dc:creator: @big_b140 big b140
item.description:
@big_b140 wrote:

[quote=“D D 3, post:8, topic:150232”]Ok here is how to add a no-ip,

Go to www.no-ip.com

Next register a account and log in,

Next go to Host/Redirects and under it it will say ADD click it and it will bring you up to a screen.

Hostname:Put what your server is called her e.g. hiyascape
Host Type:There will be a dropdown bar so if you put .biz then your server will be hiyascape.no-ip.biz
IP Address:It should so you your ip here if not go here www.whatismyip.org
Assign to Group:Leave this blank
Allow Wildcards:Leave this balnk

Leave the rest blank and click create then open your DUC and click on the little box so its checked and it will update XD[/quote]

once you do that wait about 5 minutes thats the average time it takes to show up on no-ip DUC
